name: Stressy Delivery
description:
Concept by  kungchuck - itch.io
Coding & Music by RionoxGames - itch.io

Stressy Delivery is a fast-paced speedrunning game where you play as a boy who just got a job at the post office. Your job is to deliver packages Within a a time limit. If you fail the objective your boss will be very mad. Earn money to be able to deliver the packages quicker. Follow your compass to find the way.
